The paper focuses on testing and verification of neural network algorithms in safety-critical systems, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories. The use of neural networks in control systems also relates to the systems and control (cs.SY) category. The paper also discusses defense against common cause failure, which is a topic in the cybersecurity (cs.CR) category. Finally, the paper discusses the use of neural networks in SCCPSs, which is a topic in the machine learning (cs.LG) category.
